  description: "io.open.__name__.__len__() == 4 — 'open' has 4 characters; open (4) < __exit__ (7) < readable==writable==seekable (8) < __enter__==open_code (9): open is the minimum length; confirmed Python 3.14.3 macOS"
  category: identity
  kind: python_call_eq
